{"tid":1886903,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人真係好熱情，周圍都有reception問路","createTime":"2020-02-19T08:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T15:38:49.000Z","uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10240cb978febc77d7d1a01f9b2f1c944f243f84","tid":1886903,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩係東京蕩失路，想搵間酒店休息<br />\n心諗今次大檸樂，自己一支公唔知點算好<br />\n見到無料案內所(Information)<br />\n唔知日文點解，但見到information應該係旅遊中心reception黎<br />\n入面乜都無，得條友<br />\n黎緊東京奧運，可能先起左呢啲臨時問路站<br />\n入左去問下邊到有酒店<br />\n佢好熱情咁show左個地圖俾我睇<br />\n仲打電話叫左一個人帶路<br />\n可能驚我又蕩失路<br />\n個帶路果條友仲問我what's your favourite?<br />\n雖然唔知佢咩意思，但真係幾熱情<br />\n唔講咁多住，勁攰勁眼訓依家"},{"pid":"85e0183767ca817a4882d1d8755db16c9c65d355","tid":1886903,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZWr31w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZWr31w.jpg&h=01acc82f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n休息完返香港政總先<br />\nＰＲ公司既宿敵就是我"},{"pid":"c6016e4259e66eb43d1b158d7b88dda17a478344","tid":1886903,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"相呢？"},{"pid":"433aa328ec68dec68c53e800cbcfdaa72a157990","tid":1886903,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6016e4259e66eb43d1b158d7b88dda17a478344","tid":1886903,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"相呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:16:39.000Z","msg":"希望唔好有人阻住啊叔訓教<br />\n勁攰"},{"pid":"8f88b6bc5c951d665cc18fd9470a14ec1cfafc39","tid":1886903,"uid":69289,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"6/10 Marginal Readable"},{"pid":"2c5b4d61265d09c304fc2b232adeee9a77026dff","tid":1886903,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"樓主口好臭點算"},{"pid":"fe42013510fedeacb3ea9c11